item.title: Where do u code at
item.dc:creator: @Zaron Zaron
item.description:
@Zaron wrote:

if you do not know how to run server while loading up moparscape, first you load up moparscape, but do not press start server or anything, just go into your server folder and do runserver.bat and it should say your port number, if it doesnt say “43594” then right the number that it says in file+port and then b4 the port, you gotta do start server while the runserver is started, then you just log in with any username and pass word and your on.

NOTE: You may lag if your computer isnt that fast (mine lags) 2 steps lag 2 steps lag rofl u’ll get used to it if you got a slow computer…
